ew-coronavirus-guidelines-edging-israel-closer-to-total-lockdown-1.8683889 |website=Haaretz |language=en |date=2 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{ITA}} || [[2020 Italy coronavirus lockdown]] || strong lockdown || || ||\n|-\n|{{JAP}} || || travel restrictions / entry ban || || || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.japan.travel/en/coronavirus/ |title=Coronavirus (COVID-19) advisory information &#124; Travel Japan &#124; JNTO |publisher=Japan.travel |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{JOR}} || || strong lockdown || March 14 || || <ref>{{cite news |title=Jordan Keeps Coronavirus In Check With One Of The World's Strictest Lockdowns |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/coronavirus-live-updates/2020/03/25/821349297/jordan-keeps-coronavirus-in-check-with-one-of-world-s-strictest-lockdowns |work=NPR.org |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Jordan extends coronavirus curfew, to deliver food to homes nationwide |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-jordan/jordan-extends-coronavirus-curfew-to-deliver-food-to-homes-nationwide-idUSKBN21A2J6 |website=Reuters |language=en |date=23 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{KEN}} || || evening curfew || || || <ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.nation.co.ke/counties/kisumu/Calm-as-curfew-enters-day-two/1954182-5507832-10c5elb/index.html| title=Calm as curfew enters Day Two| access-date=2020-03-30| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330161720/https://www.nation.co.ke/counties/kisumu/Calm-as-curfew-enters-day-two/1954182-5507832-10c5elb/index.html| archive-date=2020-03-30| url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{KOS}} || || curfew from 17:00 to 06:00 || || || <ref>{{cite web| url=https://seenews.com/news/kosovo-imposes-curfew-to-curb-spread-of-coronavirus-692193| title=Kosovo imposes curfew to curb spread of coronavirus| access-date=2020-03-24| url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{KWT}} || || curfew from 17:00 to 4:00 || || || <ref>{{cite web |title=Turkey, Israel Virus Cases Near 1,000; Saudi Infections Increase |url=https://www.b